@Code_Ref-Type Reproducible pipeline document (Porites evermanni lncRNA discovery)

@Code_Ref-Note See E-Peve/code/12-Peve-lncRNA-discovery.qmd

@Code_Ref 06-Ptua-lncRNA-discovery.qmd

@Code_Ref-Type Reproducible pipeline document (Pocillopora tuahiniensis lncRNA discovery)

@Code_Ref-Note See F-Ptua/code/06-Ptua-lncRNA-discovery.qmd

