@Code_Ref-Type Reproducible analysis document (Acropora pulchra lncRNA expression)

@Code_Ref-Note See D-Apul/code/03.20-D-Apul-lncRNA-expression-DESeq2.Rmd

@Data_Processing Trimming

@Data_Processing-Note Adapters and low-quality bases removed; 15bp trimmed per read

@Data_Processing Alignment

@Data_Processing-Note Reads aligned to species-specific reference genomes using HISAT2 (exon/ss guided)

@Data_Processing Assembly

@Data_Processing-Note StringTie assembly per sample followed by merged assembly; transcripts classified with gffcompare (u, x, o, i)

@Data_Processing Coding_Potential_Filtering

